title: House to Vote on Ex-Im Bank Despite Conservative Opposition (ATR - Americans for Tax Reform) ...
text: ( Source : ATR - Americans for Tax Reform ) The US House of Representatives will soon vote to reauthorize the Export-Import Bank despite the objection of key Congressional leaders including House Financial Services Chairman Jeb Hensarling
